  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\n```\r\nGiven I've been disconnected for more than 24 hours\r\nWhen I query mail server to get the messages history\r\nThen I should receive the whole history of messages\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nRecent changes on status-go mail servers are avoiding recovering messages for periods longer than 24 hours. This behavior makes queries with periods larger than 24 hours to not receive any message.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nThe user can get all messages on the app even if the messages are older than 24 hours\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nThe user doesn't get messages older than 24h.\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n\r\nQuery mail servers in batches of 24 hours instead of trying to get the whole history.\r\n",
